title: War of the Roses: There Are No Texts From His Boss
description: Ali has become suspicious of her boyfriend because he keeps suddenly running off to work because his "boss calls him in".  Well she did some snooping in his phone and saw no evidence of his boss asking him to work so  where is he going and what is he doing??
